description: This Chainlink VRF common Yulenka purrs with a rating of 67, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 67, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 1 for North, Leverage for East, 2 for South, and 3 for West. Yulenka has the personality suit of yenta. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/80671-16234-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Yulenka [67 Votes, Common]
